    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "DRYVR\u2122 Waterproofs: Uncompromising Style and Performance",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One of the standout features in the <strong>Galvin Green Concept Collection</strong> is the <strong>DRYVR\u2122 waterproof range</strong> - offering protection and style in any weather condition. At the heart of this sub-range are the <strong>ARGUS full-zip hooded jacket</strong> and <strong>ADRIAN waterproof trousers</strong>, both crafted from Pertex\u00ae Shield Stretch fabric, known for its high breathability and flexible, durable construction.</p><h4><strong>ARGUS Hooded Jacket</strong></h4><p>The ARGUS jacket is a game-changer for golfers seeking a balance of practicality and contemporary style. Available in classic Black or the distinctive Duck Green and Black combination, this jacket showcases:</p><ul><li><strong>Square Panelling Design:</strong> For a modern look that adds a touch of refinement.</li><li><strong>Adjustable Hood with Front Collar:</strong> Ensuring a snug fit that can adapt to changing weather.</li><li><strong>Enhanced Sleeve Cuffs and Functional Pockets:</strong> Designed for ease of use, whether on the course or during everyday wear.</li></ul><h4><strong>ADRIAN Trousers</strong></h4><p>Available in complementary Duck Green and Black tones, ADRIAN redefines waterproof trousers. With an elasticated waist and unique pocket-free design, they offer a sleeker silhouette compared to traditional golf trousers, allowing for a standout look both on the course and the street.</p><p>Together, the DRYVR\u2122 rainwear pieces offer a cohesive look for the modern golfer who values fashion as much as function.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
