    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "INTERFACE-1\u2122 Windproof Tops: Comfort Meets Cool",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>INTERFACE-1\u2122</strong> range brings versatile windproof layers that are as stylish as they are practical. Leading the collection is the <strong>LUKE half-zip jacket</strong>, a contemporary addition that blends effortlessly into both casual and performance settings.</p><ul><li><strong>Side Stripe Detail:</strong> A ribbed printed panel that adds a subtle yet eye-catching element.</li><li><strong>Adjustable Pullers on the Hood:</strong> Providing a customisable fit for unpredictable weather.</li><li><strong>Discreet Branding:</strong> Logos on the back and left arm for understated branding that respects both classic and contemporary styling.</li></ul><h2></h2><h2><strong>INSULA\u2122 Sweaters: Warmth with Urban Edge</strong></h2><p>As the temperature drops, the <strong>INSULA\u2122</strong> range offers stylish solutions for staying warm without compromising on aesthetics. The <strong>DIAZ and DANTE sweaters</strong> stand out as ideal choices for the style-conscious golfer looking to make a statement.</p><h4><strong>DIAZ Half-Zip Sweater</strong></h4><p>Inspired by the spray of sand from a bunker shot, the DIAZ sweater\u2019s geometric panel design brings a unique look that\u2019s both playful and refined. This half-zip option is perfect for layering and adds a sense of movement to any outfit.</p><h4><strong>DANTE Crew Neck</strong></h4><p>For a more classic look, the DANTE crew neck sweater is available in solid Duck Green, Orange, and Black. Its simplicity is its strength, making it a versatile addition that complements other pieces in the collection.</p><p>Both the DIAZ and DANTE sweaters pair perfectly with the <strong>DREW beanie hat</strong> and <strong>DEREK snood</strong> for added warmth and style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
