    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "VENTIL8\u2122 PLUS Shirts and Bottoms: Breathable and Bold",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When the game demands comfort and flexibility, the <strong>VENTIL8\u2122 PLUS</strong> line delivers. Key pieces like the <strong>MAGNUS and MIRZA polo shirts</strong> introduce bold designs with breathable fabric, ensuring players stay cool and comfortable, even under pressure.</p><ul><li><strong>Standout Patterns:</strong> Modern prints allow golfers to express their style while keeping cool on hot days.</li><li><strong>Complementary Bottoms:</strong> The <strong>NATHAN trousers</strong> and <strong>PERRY shorts</strong> complete the look, offering sturdy construction and a polished appearance.</li></ul><p>These garments capture the best of both worlds: the performance of high-tech sportswear with a fashion-forward appeal that translates effortlessly into everyday wear.</p><h3><strong>Accessories to Complete the Look</strong></h3><p>No outfit is complete without the right accessories. The <strong>Concept Collection</strong> includes thoughtful additions like the <strong>MASON t-shirt</strong> with a smart chest pocket, the <strong>SAMUEL five-panel cap</strong>, and the <strong>STANLEY bucket hat</strong>. Each piece is crafted to enhance the overall look while providing practical solutions for a golfer\u2019s everyday needs.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
